---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Code of Conduct">
  <div style="max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px 20px">
    <h1 style="font-size:28px;color:#fff;margin-bottom:16px">Code of Conduct</h1>
    <div style="font-size:14px;color:#6b7a8e;line-height:1.8">
      <p style="margin-bottom:16px">Denver Social exists to help people connect. Every member agrees to these rules.</p>
      <h3 style="font-size:18px;color:#fff;margin:20px 0 8px">The basics</h3>
      <p style="margin-bottom:8px"><b style="color:#e8ecf4">Be respectful.</b> Treat everyone the way you'd want to be treated at a friend's dinner table.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:8px"><b style="color:#e8ecf4">No harassment.</b> Zero tolerance for unwanted advances, slurs, or intimidation.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:8px"><b style="color:#e8ecf4">Show up if you RSVP.</b> No-shows hurt the group. 4 no-shows = suspended account.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:8px"><b style="color:#e8ecf4">Keep locations private.</b> Addresses are shared only with RSVPed members.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:8px"><b style="color:#e8ecf4">No soliciting.</b> This isn't a networking event or MLM opportunity.</p>
      <h3 style="font-size:18px;color:#fff;margin:20px 0 8px">One-strike policy</h3>
      <p style="margin-bottom:8px">Harassment or threatening behavior = you're out. No warnings, no second chances.</p>
      <h3 style="font-size:18px;color:#fff;margin:20px 0 8px">Reporting</h3>
      <p>Message Seth on <a href="https://discord.gg/S8SFNkdSgK" style="color:#60a5fa">Discord</a> or email <a href="mailto:stharpe98@gmail.com" style="color:#60a5fa">stharpe98@gmail.com</a>. All reports are handled privately.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
